  "remarks": "Roman Babayan is a journalist and member of the Moscow City Duma. He hosts the “Own Truth” TV show on NTV channel. He is also an editor-in-chief of “Moscow Speaks” radio. He has spread anti-Ukrainian propaganda and promoted a positive attitude to the actions of separatists in Donbas.",
